{"id":32,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":23,"title":"23. Seasons","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":29,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/23-seasons.32/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/23-seasons-2019-03-20-08-47-09/0-23-seasons.mp3","transcript":"There are four seasons.\nWinter is the cold season.\nIt snows in the winter.\nThe winds blow,\nand ice forms on the water.\nWe play hockey on the ice.\nWe play in the snow.\nAfter winter is the spring.\nThat is when it begins to get warmer.\nTrees get buds on them.\nFlowers start to bloom.\nIt rains a lot in the spring.\nSpring is followed by the summer.\nIt can get very hot in the summertime.\nThe sun shines brightly.\nWe go swimming in the summer.\nWe spend a lot of time outdoors.\nMany people go on vacations in the summer.\nWe get a summer vacation from school.\nSummer is followed by the fall or autumn.\nThe leaves on the trees change colors.\nThey change from green to red,\norange and brown.\nThe leaves fall off the trees.\nThe weather gets cooler.\nThe days get shorter.\nWe go back to school in the fall.\nThen, winter comes again.\nThe seasons follow one after each other.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:34","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"There are four seasons.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/23-seasons-2019-03-20-08-47-09/1.mp3","time_start":1.8,"time_end":3.64},{"position":2,"content":"Winter is the cold season.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/23-seasons-2019-03-20-08-47-09/2.mp3","time_start":4.2,"time_end":5.93},{"position":3,"content":"It snows in the winter.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/23-seasons-2019-03-20-08-47-09/3.mp3","time_start":6.5,"time_end":8.44},{"position":4,"content":"The winds blow,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/23-sea